Python game development. 

Requires Pyglet, Cocos2D, PyCharm and NumPy libraries.

Controls:
A,D : Move player left or right.
W : Reverse gravity
SPACE: Player jump.
M: Show/Hide menu layer.
Left Mouse Click: Attack.


